comments: Represented Sweden at the Eurovision Song Contest 1995 in Dublin, Ireland. At the close of the voting, it had received 100 points, ultimately finishing 3rd out of a possible 23. The song peaked on the Swedish Sverigetopplistan singles chart at #1 twice. On 21 April 1995 it reached #1 on the charts staying there for five weeks and then returned to #1 on 9 June 1995 for another four weeks
